UID:klang-copenhagen-open-call-2027-music-movement@artificialnouveau.github
 .io
DTSTAMP:20260723T131202Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260901
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260902
SUMMARY:Deadline: Klang Copenhagen Avantgarde Music Festival: Open Call 202
 7\, MUSIC/MOVEMENT
DESCRIPTION:Klang\, Copenhagen's avantgarde music festival\, is seeking one
  to three projects at the intersection of experimental music and movement\
 , dance or choreography for its 2027 edition at Dansehallerne. Important c
 onstraint: the call is explicitly for ready-to-go projects\, not commissio
 ns or works in progress\, so the work must already be finished and product
